4 SYNOPSIS:
5 This bill would implement a semi-monthly pay
6 plan for employees of local boards of education.
7
8
9 A BILL
10 TO BE ENTITLED
11 AN ACT
12
13 Relating to local boards of education; to provide for
14 semi-monthly salary payments of local board of education
15 employees; and to provide for local boards of education to opt
16 out of semi-monthly salary payments.
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
18 Section 1. (a) Beginning August 1, 2027, each local
19 board of education shall pay the employees of the board
20 semi-monthly one payday in arrears. Except as otherwise
21 provided in this section, salary payments based on the
22 semi-monthly plan shall be made on the first and sixteenth day
23 of each month.
24 (b) If the first or sixteenth day of any month, other
25 than the first day of October, falls on a Saturday, Sunday, or
26 holiday, then the salary payment shall be made on the last
27 workday immediately prior to the Saturday, Sunday, or holiday.
28 If the first day of October falls on a Saturday, Sunday, or
